parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden stalling of the engine can cause loss of control, accidents, or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle begins to chug like it's going to stop
then goes back to driving normally; the vehicle suddenly stops in the middle of the highway.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning instrument cluster display can cause the driver to be unaware of important safety warnings, mileage, and digital speedometer information, which can lead to accidents or other safety issues.
symptoms: The screen behind the steering wheel gets streaky and becomes unreadable.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the hill assist system can cause the vehicle to roll back, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The hill assist system does not activate
causing the vehicle to roll back.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The auto stop/start system can cause a delay in the vehicle's response to the driver's input, which can lead to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: The engine shuts off at every stop
even in traffic conditions where it may not be safe; the engine restarts with a thump; the vehicle lurches forward if the foot is not firm on the brake.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning infotainment system can cause distractions, inconvenience, and potentially lead to safety issues.
symptoms: The SD card removal message appears multiple times; the radio stops working; the phone is not connected to the car; the station is identified
but the radio does not work.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The vibration of the vehicle can cause loss of control, accidents, or discomfort for the driver and passengers.
symptoms: The front end of the vehicle shakes at 25-30 mph
but the vibration goes away after 30 mph.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning steering and lane departure system can cause loss of control, accidents, or injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle starts swaying towards the left
especially on the freeway; the tech screen issue shows a flashing green warning when there is no vehicle ahead.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission or drivetrain can cause the vehicle to hesitate, shudder, or lose power, leading to accidents or stranding the driver.
symptoms: The vehicle shudders significantly
hesitates to respond
or loses power while driving; the vehicle fails to go into park; the vehicle lurches forward unexpectedly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to shut down, lose power, or experience electrical malfunctions, leading to accidents or stranding the driver.
symptoms: The vehicle shuts down while in operation; the vehicle fails to start; electrical systems remain on despite the vehicle being shut off; warning lights illuminate on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel system can cause the vehicle to stall, lose power, or experience engine problems, leading to accidents or fires.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or shuts down while in operation; the vehicle fails to start; a solid check engine light illuminates; the fuel pump flow issue causes cars to stall and not turn on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the braking system can cause the vehicle to lose braking ability, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The braking system becomes impossible to use while operating; the vacuum pump fails
affecting braking performance.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the engine performance can cause the vehicle to lose power, hesitate, or experience reduced engine performance, leading to accidents or stranding the driver.
symptoms: The engine power is reduced; the vehicle hesitates or loses power; the turbocharger overboost warning illuminates.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the infotainment system can cause distractions while driving, leading to accidents, and can also result in the loss of important vehicle functions such as navigation and climate control.
symptoms: The touch screen display goes black
the touch screen display does not show GPS information
the instrument panel does not display readings
the SD card error message appears
the radio turns on at maximum volume
the backup camera remains on
and the infotainment center becomes unresponsive.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause unexpected shutdowns, loss of critical vehicle functions, and potentially lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle fails to restart
multiple warning messages appear on the dashboard
the vehicle shuts down while driving
the power locks malfunction
and the radio cuts off.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the BCM can cause a range of electrical system malfunctions, leading to unexpected shutdowns, loss of critical vehicle functions, and potentially leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Multiple warning messages appear on the dashboard
the vehicle fails to restart
and the side detection system becomes inoperable.
